WHISKARITA raced from the second flight while four wide, sat in striking position outside in the backstretch, was no match for the eventual winner and finished clearly second best. FAVORITE trailed the field early, swung out into the final turn, and improved position in the drive. WHITEROSE SPIRIT vied four wide into the opening turn, stalked the pace while three wide, challenged the front leaving the backstretch, and was caught late. WHEELSUPINTHIRTY attended the early pace from just off the rail, led the way into the backstretch, and was overtaken and faded steadily. LITTLE HARPER opted to sit just off the pace while three wide leaving the opening turn, and tired early. MIDNIGHT GARDEN was outsprinted to the opening turn, and lacked interest.

RACE.FOOTNOTES: BARE BACK JACK stalked the early pacesetters, raced in close quarters leaving the backstretch in the three path, drove three wide into the stretch and narrowly prevailed. ESTIFRAAD saved ground early, cut the corner into the stretch, and was outfinished. THE BEAT trailed the field early, gained closer order nearing the last turn, and closed gamely to score show. COMMON KNOWLEDGE dueled for the early lead, inherited an advantage leaving the backstretch, and came up empty in the drive. BORKAN stalked the dueling pacesetters while three to four wide, and lacked a closing response needed. AMUSING WAY contested the lead inside of COMMON KNOWLEDGE and tired early.

RACE.FOOTNOTES: MISSCZECH broke alertly, saved ground while showing the way, drew clear nearing the final turn, and held late. PLUM BLUE unhurried early, gained closer order gradually through the backstretch, advanced quickly inside in the final turn, was gaining ground through the stretch on MISSCZECH and missed. DANCE SHOES sat in striking position from the two path, went in pursuit of MISSCZEH but lacked the closing response that was needed. TONE IT UP saved ground and lacked a kick. MINE ME raced three wide through the opening turn, was unable to move on with the field and gave way. ORANGE THEORY tracked inside, and tired early.
